Stream editor

Awk examples

awk pattern-directed scanning and processing language

Authors: Aho, Weinberger, Kernighan

:

  • awk '{print NR "\t" $0}'
  • awk 'END{print NR}'
  • awk '{print $2, $1}'
  • awk '{s=0; for (i=1; i<=NF; i++) s=s+$i; print s}'
  • awk '{sub(/[ \t]+$/, "")};1' ""
  • awk '{l=length();s=int((79-l)/2); printf "%"(s+l)"s\n",$0}' filename
